### Create a new Custom Trip Request (Lead)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/custom-trip-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "numPeople": 2,
    "budgetMin": 1000,
    "budgetMax": 5000,
    "startDate": "2024-05-01",
    "endDate": "2024-05-10",
    "preferences": "We love hiking and local food.",
    "source": "curate",
    "status": "new"
}

